<text>The Grammy Award for Best Soul Gospel Performance, Contemporary was awarded from 1978 to 1983. A similar award, the Grammy Award for Best Contemporary Soul Gospel Album has been awarded since 1991. 

Years reflect the year in which the Grammy Awards were presented, for works released in the previous year.

