where:
* formula_12 is the laminar flow Darcy friction factor (SI units: dimensionless)
* formula_13 is the Reynolds number (SI units: dimensionless)
* formula_14 is the Hedstrom number (SI units: dimensionless)

The Reynolds number and the Hedstrom number are respectively defined as:
